docs {
  # Get Cable TV Packages
  
  Use this endpoint after the user selects a provider.
  
  Query:
  
  `provider`
  Required. Use `DSTV`, `GOTV`, or `STARTIMES`.
  
  The backend fetches packages from VTpass and applies BillXpress markup to return `sellingPrice`.
}
